title: When Stars Align: Famous Friends
description:
Everyone can use a good friend; someone to cheer us up when we’re feeling down, someone to inspire and motivate us, or sometimes, simply someone to keep us company. Famous people are no different than any of us when it comes to the importance of friendship. Perhaps that’s why we get a big kick out of it when we see the stars palling around.

May we all enjoy a friendship or two like these.
